# else-with-colon regression (synthetic). The worker senses a cube WEST, so the
# TRUE branch must run (step w onto the hole = exit). A parser that treats
# "else:" as a label falls through into the else body and steps east instead.
name Else Colon
dim 5 1
ent hole 0 0
ent cube 1 0 7
ent worker 2 0
ent wall 4 0
goal all_exited
